OL,3,CPower workers accept new pay offer
OL,4,Cafter industrial action
OL,6,FPower workers at Sellafield have
OL,7,Faccepted an increased pay offer after
OL,8,F15 days of industrial action earlier
OL,9,Fthis month.
OL,11,FUp to 40 Unite union members, employed
OL,12,Fby PX Limited, took part in 15 days of
OL,13,Findustrial action short of strikes
OL,14,Ffrom 1 August 2024.
OL,16,FThe union members work at the Fellside
OL,17,FCombined Heat and Power plant which
OL,18,Fprovides electricity and steam to
OL,19,FSellafield.
