OL,3,CPower workers accept new pay offer
OL,4,Cafter industrial action
OL,6,FThey accepted a pay rise of between 6%
OL,7,Fand 7.5% starting from May 2024.
OL,9,FIn previous pay discussions, the
OL,10,Foffers varied between 3% and 4.5%. The
OL,11,Fworkers undertake a range of roles
OL,12,Fincluding shift managers, operators,
OL,13,Felectrical and instrumentation
OL,14,Ftechnicians and administrators.
OL,16,FUnite said it would now be working to
OL,17,Fsign a recognition agreement with the
OL,18,Fcompany.
